In Logic you can use a feature called '''Bounce in Place''' to bounce individual track regions easily and quickly in a manner that automatically replaces the old regions time placement.

 
Hold down '''Control''' and click the region. Choose '''Bounce and Merge / Bounce in Place'''


[[File:Logic bounce in place.png]]



A dialog box will appear with customizable settings. Set them how you want them and click '''OK'''


[[File:Logic bounce in place dialog box.png]]


